UltraTerminal Videotex Integration
==================================

This subtree contains the UltraTerminal-facing Videotex runtime derived from
the local vidtex-master source tree. The upstream project is a GPLv3 ncurses
Viewdata/Videotex-over-IP client. UltraTerminal keeps the protocol decoder,
Mode 7 character mapping, built-in service profile data, raw frame capture
state, and keyboard transforms, but replaces the ncurses/socket frontend with
an in-process runtime that renders into UltraTerminal's existing text and
attribute buffers.

Files copied verbatim:

* COPYING
* UPSTREAM-README.md
* vidtexrc

Adapted runtime files:

* ultra_vidtex.h
* ultra_vidtex.c

The copied/adapted Videotex code remains under GPLv3 terms from the upstream
vidtex source. Commercial/private distribution clearance is intentionally not
encoded in the build system; that decision remains external to the port.
